sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Token as Token Contract (ERC20)
    participant Lending as SimpleLending Contract

    Note over User, Token: Step 1: User gives permission
    User->>Token: approve(SimpleLending_Address, 1000)
    Token-->>User: Transaction Confirmed (Allowance Set)

    Note over User, Lending: Step 2: User performs action
    User->>Lending: supply(1000)
    
    Note over Lending, Token: Step 3: Lending contract pulls tokens
    Lending->>Token: transferFrom(User, Lending, 1000)
    Token->>Token: Check Allowance >= 1000
    Token->>Token: Transfer 1000 from User to Lending
    Token->>Token: Decrease Allowance
    Token-->>Lending: Returns True
    
    Lending-->>User: Supply Successful